{"tid":2242830,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"管浩鳴現身金鐘幫陳同佳申請赴台簽證 我相信我所做的一切對得住天地良心","createTime":"2020-10-14T09:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T14:28:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"5d54c7ccda856ad3b88f4b7081096d2ef2ccd58e","tid":2242830,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:51:54.000Z","msg":"下午大約4時，一直協助陳同佳的管浩鳴前往金鐘力寶中心的台北經濟文化辦事處（香港），其間他手持一個透明公文袋，裡面放有一堆文件、一個香港聖公會教省辦事處的信封、一張入台申請書、一張香港身份證及一本特區護照，其中入台申請書上的簽名為陳同佳，相信是為陳同佳申請赴台簽證。他逗留大約10分鐘後離開，其間被問及「申請情況點呀」，管牧只回應：「我返去同律師商量下先」。有記者再向管牧查詢起行機會「大唔大」，他則表示：「唔知呀，真係唔知呀&hellip;照我知同佳將啲資料畀咗台灣律師，但律師點處理，我估佢有自己應該嘅途徑」。<br />\n<br />\n其後，管牧再就事件回應：「我相信我所做的一切對得住天地良心。你們認為『公事』或『私事』我不想爭拗。我只是暫時無法回答大家問題。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201014/LVTWDM2IMVHMFK4JG3W2RIVL6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201014%2FLVTWDM2IMVHMFK4JG3W2RIVL6U%2F&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2uBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=72a1f630\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20201014%2FLVTWDM2IMVHMFK4JG3W2RIVL6U%2F&h=5cd4b6c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20201014/LVTWDM2IMVHMFK4JG3W2RIVL6U/</a>"},{"pid":"902c66073daa4440f87a942741258a3f531ad03d","tid":2242830,"uid":82359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:52:40.000Z","msg":"落地獄啦你"},{"pid":"ae3248577bdb2407cf5d859ecc109e84394310e5","tid":2242830,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:53:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7298660097120c0e4e93aaf041d3180a3ac7fc33","tid":2242830,"uid":177727,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"其實佢哋兩個咩關係？唔係代言人又成日發言？"},{"pid":"facfaf